{"tid":1810922,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[居安思危] 中共：香港人一定鬼打鬼","createTime":"2020-01-04T09:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T09:40:55.000Z","uid":286309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2720a3c0ef8aa65c9cc48e0ef7327a5214882320","tid":1810922,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wsGDHBSeqrM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwsGDHBSeqrM&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=4cee19c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wsGDHBSeqrM</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然呢條片係講有關台灣「反滲透法」嘅觀點，看似唔關香港事<br />\n不過其中一點，好適合俾我地思考：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立理性思辯，不落入簡化</span><span style=\"color: green;\">「二元對立」</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4SDKSg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4SDKSg.png&h=ef75ca77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J5ee2v9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ5ee2v9.png&h=45b44efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n套用翻香港情況就係<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「2020普選」＋「備戰功能組別」<br />\n「五大訴求」＋「香港獨立」</div><br />\n<br />\n以上嘅手段嘅最終目的只有一個<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港人要楂旗，自己香港自己救</strong></span></div><br />\n記住<br />\n我地嘅目標得一個，就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">光復香港</span></strong></span><br />\n記住<br />\n方法可以唔一樣，絕對唔可以鬼打鬼<br />\n記住<br />\n手段可以好多，目的卻只有一個，唔好淨用手段去估對方嘅政治取態<br />\n<br />\n你一句<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「泛登仔」</span></strong>；我一句<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「熱狗」</strong></span><br />\n真心講出運動問題所在就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「分化」</span></strong>；支持上街抗爭就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「送頭」</span></strong><br />\n我估每個都聽得多，總之我地要贏嘅唯有不斷進化<br />\n睇多啲聽多啲，不落入簡化「二元對立」，最好就係互相合作<br />\n最後睇多次伍公子條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gmDCAkJMxQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgmDCAkJMxQw&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=cd9309ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gmDCAkJMxQw</a>"},{"pid":"c6f3e1aac4b0e1a37f97a45355c3b53d99deebe2","tid":1810922,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f1191cdd82991b5dbec593f0e85f0323296e677","tid":1810922,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:40:55.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}